quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Tsoka kwa aliyense amene amajeda ndi kuononga mbiri ya anzake
  104,2,Amene amasonkhanitsa chuma chake ndi kumachiwerenga
  104,3,Iye amaganiza kuti chuma chake chidzamuchititsa iye kukhala ndi moyo wamuyaya
  104,4,Iyayi! Ndithudi iye adzaponyedwa ku moto woononga
  104,5,Kodi chidzakuuza kuti moto woononga ndi chiyani
  104,6,Ndi moto wa Mulungu umene Mwini wake anauyatsa
  104,7,Umene umafuka m’mitima ya anthu
  104,8,Ndithudi udzawatsekereza mbali iliyonse
  104,9,M’sanamila zoima